"&kfourinline; is a board game for two players based on the &nbsp;"
"<trademark>Connect-Four</trademark> game."
msgstr ""
"&kfourinline; jest grą planszową przeznaczoną dla dwóch graczy, opartąna "
"grze <trademark>Połącz-Cztery</trademark>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:88
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The players try to build up a row of four pieces using different "
#| "strategies. Pieces are placed on a board. The game can also be played "
